# CODEOWNERS — the authoritative review-routing layer per ADR-034:
# the tool classifies changes; GitHub's branch protection + these rules
# enforce the human review. Seeded by tools/bootstrap-data-repo.sh;
# regenerate from the manifest's role map when manifest.toml lands.

# Registry data: every change is a PR; destructive classes
# (delete/void/header per ADR-016) additionally surface in the
# pr-check annotation. Approvers own the data root.
*                       __APPROVERS__

# Governance surfaces are stricter by construction — contract/manifest
# edits are CODEOWNERS-gated paths (ADR-033/034).
/.part-registry/        __APPROVERS__
/.github/               __APPROVERS__
